{"tid":487311,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone x 面部資料派街坊","createTime":"2017-12-02T16:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T16:42:37.000Z","uid":77973,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2ecd7ae61f724af5a6d17bd057bb8ef5b63c193d","tid":487311,"uid":77973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:00:30.000Z","msg":"在 iPhone X 上面新加入的 Face ID 功能，採用的是其 TrueDepth 相機所獲取的立體臉部數據，雖然 Face ID 本身有相當嚴格的加密，但其實 Apple 亦同時容許第三方開發者存取 TrueDepth 相機的數據，意味其他 App 也可以掃描到用家的臉部特徵自用。<br />\n<br />\n最近有關注私隱的團體表示，注意到 Apple 原來容許第三方開發者使用並存取 TrueDepth 相機，意味着這些第三方 App 可以擁有相當仔細的用家臉部數據，其中包括即時讀取眼皮、口部和其他部位的 52 種細微動作特徵，配合全立體臉部掃描數據。這雖然本身是容許第三方開發者可以使用這個新功能，帶來更多特別的應用，例如相當受歡迎的即時人臉濾鏡特效，但私隱團體擔心這些開發者如果把數據上載到自己的伺服器儲存，其實會帶來私隱方面的危險。<br />\n<br />\nApple 方面有私隱政策，規定使用 TrueDepth 功能的 App 必須同時擁有自己的私隱政策和用戶同意書，並且清楚列明會收集什麼數據和怎樣使用，但結果而言其實容易出現漏網之魚，用戶也不一定會細讀私隱政策。Apple 方面只回應表示，他們向來注重用戶的私隱，從他們在 Face ID 上加入的保安即可看到他們對私隱的重視。而在功能自由度及私隱之間的平衡向來不容易，以後用家在容許第三方 App 使用相機的時候，也要特別留神了。<br />\n<br />\n來源：MacRumors<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/unwirehk[url][/url]/posts/10159923785015495[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funwirehk%5Burl%5D%5B%2Furl%5D%2Fposts%2F10159923785015495%5B%2Furl%5D&d=NztypxuZbm0QUhDvt%2FI628mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=b540f7a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/unwirehk[url][/url]/posts/10159923785015495[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟驚都未驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，希望app開發商公開所有IPhone x users' face detail比全世界<br />\n<br />\nPosted via Samsung Galaxy S8+ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9b2b8d8e458e1c22fb8423a48710d2cbce6f15","tid":487311,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81a0de9e6e9e156dd02bb9c81995528c18b1c492","tid":487311,"uid":22507,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"出街夠俾人見到啦<br />\n咪揀出街囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdf758cfddbaf81b58766ec206c6fa3fb21270e","tid":487311,"uid":158660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:08:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f72a749c7a8529b13e5d07592c60e8a63095509","tid":487311,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:11:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a5604626ae200eb5c027a7ec722f35b12c54768","tid":487311,"uid":45471,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出街夠俾人見到啦<br />\n咪揀出街囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜柒理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4006841cf9e08fbd4152b39eecefee7289cbc2","tid":487311,"uid":16904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T16:42:37.000Z","msg":"見到topic, 即刻嬲到send左email俾apple投訴<br />\n點知內文又無證實到係派街坊<br />\n聽講apple好小氣的，希望樓豬無事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}